title: (Weds Part 2) Bobby’s New Fantasy + Country Guitar Solo Game
itunes:title: (Weds Part 2) Bobby’s New Fantasy + Country Guitar Solo Game
description:
Bobby shares a new fantasy he has…and things get weird. It involves something happening on Saturday. Bobby plays a solo from a no. 1 country song and Amy and Eddie have to guess the song. We also take callers who share their engagement ring stories in response to the mailbag.
